  "title": "Driver Chauffeur",
  "description": "<p>Driver Chauffeur</p><p>Working Hours:<br />• Monday - Saturday<br />• 9.00am – 6.00pm</p><p>Job Responsibilities:<br />• To chauffeur the Chairman & family, colleagues, clients and guests to and from various locations within Singapore.</p><p>• To maintain cleanliness of vehicle, both interior and exterior, including car washing, regular servicing and vehicle inspection.</p><p>• To perform dispatch duties, including running errands and fulfilling ad-hoc requests as required by the company.</p><p>• Maintain professionalism and confidentiality at all times, providing a positive representation of the company.</p><p>• To assist in administrative duties when require.</p><p>• Perform other ad-hoc duties when assigned.</p><p><br />Job Requirements:<br />• Valid Class 3 driving license with good driving record.<br />• Must have relevant working experience, able to drive luxury cars / MPV. <br />• Familiar with Singapore roads and landmarks.<br />• Willing to perform overtime hours as and when required (including weekend and public holiday). <br />• Good interpersonal skills and attitude, reliable and responsible. <br />• Able to speak in Mandarin (as need to liaise with Mandarin speaking clients)</p><p>Please email your detailed resume stating current and expected salary via APPLY NOW below.</p>",
